---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import FAQSchema from "../../../components/FAQSchema.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Carpet Cleaning Longueuil | Carpet & Upholstery Specialists"
  description="The #1 expert in carpet and furniture cleaning in Longueuil. Fast truck-mount service for Old Longueuil, Saint-Hubert, and Greenfield Park."
>
  <!-- SPLIT SCREEN HERO -->
  <div class="split-hero-container">
    <div class="container full-width-split">
      <div class="split-layout">
        <!-- LEFT COLUMN: CONTENT (Hook) -->
        <div class="split-content fade-in-section">
          <span class="service-cat-badge">THE SOUTH SHORE HUB • LONGUEUIL</span>
          <h1 class="split-title fade-in-up text-gradient-empire">
            Carpet & Sofa Cleaning in Longueuil
          </h1>

          <div class="problem-statement fade-in-up delay-100" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent);">
            <h3 class="problem-title" style="color: var(--color-primary);">One City, Different Needs:</h3>
            <p class="problem-text">
              From the beautiful century-old homes of Old Longueuil to the growing residential developments of Saint-Hubert, your carpets and furniture accumulate road dust from Route 132, seasonal allergens, and daily dirt brought in by family and pets.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="lead-text fade-in-up delay-200">
            Empire Cleaning Group is the trusted choice for Longueuil residents. Our certified technicians deploy the raw extraction power of our truck-mount units to remove 99% of bacteria, revive the colors of your area rugs, and breathe new life into your fabric or leather sofas.
          </p>

          <div class="cta-group fade-in-up delay-300">
            <a href="tel:5148939939" class="btn btn-gradient-green pulse-btn">
              <span class="icon">📞</span> (514) 893-9939 (Longueuil Service)
            </a>
            <button
              onclick="window.openEstimationWidget()"
              class="btn btn-gradient-green"
            >
              <span class="icon">⚡</span> Free Online Quote
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: IMAGE (Visual / Slideshow) -->
        <div class="split-image-wrapper fade-in-section delay-200">
          <div class="slideshow-container">
             <img
              src="/images/catalog/team-nettoyage-empire.webp"
              alt="The Empire Cleaning Group expert team ready to serve Longueuil"
              class="slide active"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              fetchpriority="high"
              loading="eager"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/camion-usine-nettoyage-empire.webp"
              alt="Our industrial steam extraction truck-mount in action"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/nettoyage-tapis-laine-jaune.webp"
              alt="Professional wool rug cleaning in Longueuil"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
             <img
              src="/images/catalog/nettoyage-fauteuil-professionnel.webp"
              alt="Stunning result on a living room sofa after professional cleaning"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="image-overlay-gradient"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout">
        <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
        <div class="service-main">
          <!-- BENEFIT LIST & SEO CONTENT -->
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-100">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              The Empire Difference for Covers and Carpets
            </h2>

            <p>
              In Longueuil, why rent a small pharmacy machine when you can get industrial-grade results right at home? Here is our comprehensive approach:
            </p>

            <ul class="benefit-list" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
              <li>
                <strong>Wall-to-Wall Carpets & Stairs:</strong> Constant traffic on your stairs crushes the fibers. Our enzymatic pre-treatment followed by ultra-hot water extraction (over 200°F) lifts the pile and removes abrasive grit hidden deep at the base of your carpet.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Furniture Care (Sofas, Chairs, Mattresses):</strong> Your family sectional is the centerpiece of your living room. We adjust our water pressure and temperature to gently clean microfiber, cotton, velvet, and even leather—stripping away body oils and food stains.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Severe Odor Removal (Urine & Smoke):</strong> Unlike typical commercial deodorizers that just mask smells, we inject bacterial enzymes that organically digest pet uric acid crystals or deeply embedded smoke from textiles.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Area Rugs & Orientals:</strong> Cleaning an authentic wool rug requires a low-pH chemical balance. We wash delicate area rugs with zero risk of dye bleeding, all while preserving the natural oils of the wool.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>The Truck-Mount Advantage:</strong> All the heavy and noisy machinery stays parked outside. We only bring our steam and vacuum hoses inside your home. The dirt is extracted directly into our truck's wastewater tank for sanitary disposal, protecting your home's drains.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
               <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                ⏱️ Ultra-Fast Drying Time
              </h3>
              <p>
                A major complaint with amateur cleaning services is carpets remaining soaking wet for two days, often developing a musty "wet dog" smell.
              </p>
              <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                Our powerful industrial vacuum blowers recover up to 95% of the injected moisture. Your carpets and upholstery in Longueuil are typically completely dry and ready for use in just <strong>3 to 6 hours</strong>.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
              <hr class="separator" />
              <h3>Fast Dispatch on the South Shore</h3>
              <p>
                Because Longueuil is the central hub of the South Shore, several of our trucks are circulating there daily. Whether you need a massive spring cleaning or have an emergency (like a red wine spill right before a party), we often have same-day or next-day availability.
              </p>
               <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                Explore our <a href="/en/tips" style="color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: bold;">Expert Blog</a> to discover maintenance tips specifically tailored to your fabrics.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NEW SECTIONS: BENEFITS & FAQ -->
  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout" style="display: block;">
        <div class="service-main" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
           
           <!-- ZONES DESSERVIES -->
          <div class="zones-section" style="margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem;">Longueuil Boroughs We Cover</h3>

             <div class="city-group">
              <div class="badges-container">
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Old Longueuil (Vieux-Longueuil)</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Saint-Hubert (Laflèche / Parc-de-la-Cité area)</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Greenfield Park</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Brossard (Nearby)</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Boucherville (Nearby)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="contact-footer">Speak with one of our Longueuil agents: <strong>(514) 893-9939</strong>.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ -->
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-300" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Frequently Asked Questions — Longueuil Cleaning
            </h2>
            <FAQSchema
              faqs={[
                 {
                  question:
                    "I live in an older heritage home in Old Longueuil with very narrow carpeted stairs. Can you safely clean them?",
                  answer:
                    "Yes. We use specialized handheld extraction tools designed specifically for stair treads and risers, allowing us to deeply clean even the narrowest heritage staircases without damaging the surrounding woodwork.",
                },
                {
                  question:
                    "How long does it take to clean a 6-seat sectional and three carpeted bedrooms in Saint-Hubert?",
                  answer:
                    "Thanks to the raw efficiency of our truck-mount system and experienced technicians, a job like that generally takes between 2.5 and 3.5 hours. We maximize our setup time to be extremely efficient.",
                },
                {
                   question:
                    "My children suffer from allergies. Are your upholstery cleaning products truly safe?",
                  answer:
                    "Absolutely. Our core cleaning solutions are classified as non-toxic, biodegradable, and free of dangerous VOCs (volatile organic compounds). Furthermore, our hot water rinsing step guarantees that zero sticky soap residue is ever left behind in your sofa fibers.",
                },
                {
                  question:
                    "Do you service large condo buildings in Greenfield Park where the truck hoses cannot reach?",
                  answer:
                    "Yes, for high-rise units where the distance exceeds the capacity of our truck hoses (over 200 feet), we deploy our heavy-duty industrial portable extractors, delivering professional-grade performance right inside your apartment.",
                }
              ]}
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide");
  if (slides.length > 0) {
    let currentSlide = 0;
    setInterval(() => {
      slides[currentSlide].classList.remove("active");
      currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % slides.length;
      slides[currentSlide].classList.add("active");
    }, 4000);
  }
</script>

<style>
  /* Base styles reused for consistency */
  .split-hero-container { background-color: #fff; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; overflow: hidden; width: 100vw; }
  .full-width-split { width: 100%; max-width: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .split-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; align-items: stretch; min-height: 80vh; }
  .split-content { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 100px 4rem 4rem 10%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .service-cat-badge { text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 0.85rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .split-title { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 3.5vw, 4rem); color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.1; }
  .city-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .badges-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .badge { padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; border: 1px solid transparent; }
  .badge-blue { background: #e8f4fd; border-color: #c5dff0; }
  .problem-statement { background: #ffffff; border-left: 4px solid #ff4444; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(174, 206, 235, 0.3); }
  .problem-title { font-size: 1rem; color: #cc0000; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; }
  .problem-text { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-main); font-style: italic; }
  .lead-text { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-main); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 650px; }
  .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .cta-group { display: none !important; } }
  .split-image-wrapper { position: relative; height: 100%; min-height: 500px; width: 100%; }
  .slideshow-container { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; }
  .slideshow-container img.slide {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100% !important;
    height: 100% !important;
    object-fit: cover !important;
    object-position: center !important;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;
  }
  .slideshow-container img.slide.active { opacity: 1; }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .split-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .split-content { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; order: 1; }
    .split-image-wrapper { order: 2; height: 400px; min-height: 0; }
    .lead-text { max-width: 100%; }
  }
  .service-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 5rem; }
  .section-title { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; display: inline-block; }
  .separator { border: 0; height: 1px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .benefit-list { margin: 2rem 0; list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .benefit-list li { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .benefit-list li::before { content: "✓"; color: #d32f2f; position: absolute; left: 0; font-weight: bold; }
  .contact-footer { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: #666; }
</style>
